data.description: This beautiful home boasts an open floor plan that encompasses dark wood floors and sleek ceramic tiles while the kitchen offers granite countertops and stainless steel appliances with a double oven. Enjoy your backyard with its pool and take shade under your covered patio while you entertain guests. Its move in ready with brand new painted interior, new energy efficient AC unit (2020) and new roof (2018). Convenient to the Forum shopping center, nightly entertainment, Randolph AFB, I-35 and Hwy 1604. Transferable 3.65% VA loan may be available for qualified buyers. NO HOA!
